ploads/2024/07/JPEGMAFIA.-Credit_-Michael-Hickey_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/JPEGMAFIA.-Credit_-Michael-Hickey_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/JPEGMAFIA.-Credit_-Michael-Hickey_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/JPEGMAFIA.-Credit_-Michael-Hickey_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jpegmafia">JPEGMAFIA</a>分享了他的全新单曲“Sin Miedo”，请在下面查看。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/jpegmafia-lp-interview-age-britney-spears-rap-3084521">JPEGMAFIA：“我并不是想与众不同。我天生就与众不同”</a></strong></li></ul><p> 《Sin Medio》（翻译过来就是“无所畏惧”）是 JPEGMAFIA 今年的第二张个人单曲。这首歌曲以 2 Live Crew 的《Hoochie Mama》样本为基础，利用金属吉他融合了摇滚、嘻哈、电子和舞曲。</p><p>这是这位说唱歌手自 2021 年以来首张个人专辑，紧随 6 月 17 日发行的单曲《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iStiV1eBiV8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">don&#39;t reliance on other men</a> 》。</p><p> 《Sin Miedo》伴随着一段类似的喧闹音乐视频，其中 JPEGMAFIA 戴着牛仔帽开车兜风，并在高速公路立交桥下表演——所有这些都以一种令人迷失方向、故障的风格拍摄。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="JPEGMAFIA - SIN MIEDO" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SpH83KzVKDc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> JPEGMAFIA 去年首次宣布他正在制作一张专辑，并告诉歌迷<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jpegmafia-says-he-will-release-three-albums-in-2023-3385764">他们可以期待他在 2023 年推出三张专辑</a>。</p><p>然而，他只发布了一个与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/danny-brown">丹尼·布朗</a>合作的完整项目，名为“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jpegmafia-and-danny-brown-announce-collaborative-album-sharing-the-hoes-share-single-3412713">SCARING THE HOES: VOL 1”</a> 。随后，两人又推出了四轨 EP“Scaring the Hoes: DLC Pack”。</p><p> 6月17日，他在Instagram上向粉丝确认，备受期待的第二张个人专辑即将发行，并写道：“专辑在路上”。</p><p>这位说唱歌手的真名是巴林顿·德沃恩·亨德里克斯 (Barrington DeVaughn Hendricks)，上一次发行个人专辑是在 2021 年。《LP!》获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jpegmafia-lp-album-review-denzel-curry-bald-britney-spears-3076252"><em>NME</em>的四星好评</a>，赞扬了他的艺术专注。</p><p> “JPEGMafia 被低估了，因为他不像大狗那样创作音乐，但无论如何，JPEGMafia 仍然保持着他的正直——在这个过程中不断地拿出高标准的工作。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C8U-3M4yt9i/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.8