 Rob Reiner 预计《Spinal Tap II》将于 2025 年“春季或夏季”上映https://www.nme.com/news/film/rob-reiner-expects-spinal-tap-ii-to-be-released-in-spring-or-summer-2025-3776600?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign= rob-reiner 预计 Spinal-tap-ii 将于 2025 年春季或夏季发布Max PilleySat, 20 Jul 2024 10:38:14 +0000 Film NewsNewsComedyRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3776600 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/spinal_tap_reiner.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/spinal_tap_reiner.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/spinal_tap_reiner-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/spinal_tap_reiner-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/spinal_tap_reiner-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/spinal_tap_reiner-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/spinal_tap_reiner-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 1984 年的《This Is Spinal Tap》续集将由保罗·麦卡特尼、埃尔顿·约翰和拉斯·乌尔里希出演</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/rob-reiner-expects-spinal-tap-ii-to-be-released-in-spring-or-summer-2025-3776600">Rob Reiner 预计《Spinal Tap II》将于 2025 年“春季或夏季”发布的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/spinal_tap_reiner.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/spinal_tap_reiner.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/spinal_tap_reiner-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/spinal_tap_reiner-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/spinal_tap_reiner-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/spinal_tap_reiner-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/spinal_tap_reiner-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>导演 Rob Reiner 表示，他预计期待已久的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spinal-tap"><i>Spinal Tap II</i></a>将于 2025 年“春季或夏季”上映。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="345" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/this-is-spinal-tap-2-preview-rob-reiner-sequel-3234361"><b>《This Is Spinal Tap 2》：这是 Rob Reiner 告诉我们的关于期待已久的续集的内容</b></a></li></ul><p>1984 年备受喜爱的纪录片<i>《This Is Spinal Tap》</i>被认为是有史以来最伟大的喜剧电影之一，克里斯托弗·盖斯特 (Christopher Guest)、迈克尔·麦基恩 (Michael McKean) 和哈利·希勒 (Harry Shearer) 饰演了这对倒霉的重金属三人组。</p><p>这三位演员都将在这部备受期待的续集中回归，导演雷纳（《<i>当哈利遇到莎莉》</i> 、 <i>《伴我同行》</i> 、 <i>《公主新娘</i>》）也将在这部备受期待的续集中回归，雷纳也将在影片中重新扮演虚构的导演马蒂·迪伯吉。 </p><figure id="attachment_3234370" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3234370" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3234370" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/spinal-tap-1984.jpg" alt="脊椎水龙头" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/spinal-tap-1984.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/spinal-tap-1984-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/spinal-tap-1984-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/spinal-tap-1984-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/spinal-tap-1984-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/spinal-tap-1984-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3234370" class="wp-caption-text"> Christopher Guest、Michael McKean 和 Harry Shearer 在《This Is Spinal Tap》中，1984 年（图片来源：Everett Collection Inc / Alamy Stock Photo）</figcaption></figure><p>续集于 2022 年首次宣布，在接受<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/07/albert-brooks-defending-my-life-emmy-nominations-2024-rob-reiner-spinal-tap-update-1236013731/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>Deadline</i></a>采访时，雷纳就电影的进展提供了重要的最新信息。</p><p> “进展顺利，”他说。 “我们对家人和朋友的第一次放映可能会在八月，然后在九月的某个时候我们将开始向发行商展示它，我们希望在明年春末或初夏的某个时候推出它。”</p><p>他补充说，目前在新奥尔良的拍摄工作已经结束。</p><p>在过去的几年里，有关这部电影的一些信息不断被泄露，最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/lars-ulrich-and-chad-smith-to-cameo-in-this-is-spinal-tap-sequel-3609970">有消息称，Metallica 的 Lars Ulrich 和 Red Hot Chili Peppers 的 Chad Smith 将在片中露面</a>。</p><p>鉴于 Spinal Tap 在长期雇用鼓手方面的传奇记录，粉丝们可能会认为这些鼓手只不过是短暂的客串。</p><p> <i>《Spinal Tap II》</i>中确认的其他名字包括回归的 Fran Drescher 和 Paul Shaffer，以及新名字 John Michael Higgins、Chris Addison、Kerry Godliman 和 Nina Conti。</p><p>此前有消息称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/paul-mccartney-elton-john-to-star-this-is-spinal-tap-sequel-3549741">保罗·麦卡特尼和埃尔顿·约翰将出现在影片中</a>，雷纳本人也证实了这一消息。</p><p>这就是原版<i>《This Is Spinal Tap》</i>的文化遗产，乐队继续为落入电影陷阱的前景所困扰。例如，《Talking Heads <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/talking-heads-didnt-want-stop-making-sense-film-to-be-too-spinal-tap-3765641">》最近谈到了他们为防止<i>《Stop Making Sense》</i>变得“过于脊椎敲击”而做出的努力</a>。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-spinal-taps-derek-smalls-return-with-new-single-must-crush-barbie-3498619]">Spinal Tap 的 Derek Smalls（希勒）发行了他五年来的第一首新单曲“Must Crush Barbie”</a> 。他将格蕾塔·葛韦格的这部红极一时的电影描述为“温水的化身”，并在歌曲中唱到这部电影“粉红色太多”，他称之为浪费“电影和墨水”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/rob-reiner-expects-spinal-tap-ii-to-be-released-in-spring-or-summer-2025-3776600">Rob Reiner 预计《Spinal Tap II》将于 2025 年“春季或夏季”发布的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
